Q. Do you know who snatched it - A. Yes, the prisoner is the man. it was about a quarter after seven on the 9th of January, I was just turning the corner of Mercer street, he came on one side of me, and snatched the shawl off my shoulders, I had a momentary sight of the prisoner; I have never seen my shawl since, I am quite certain of the prisoner; I ran after the prisoner;
William Roberts
stopped the prisoner.
